":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1N","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":14606,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/06\/tawhid-then-muhammad-wills\/","url_meta":{"origin":111,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: What Allah wills, then what Muhammad wills","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Tufayl reported: A man among the idolaters said to a man among the Muslims, \"How excellent it would be of your people if you said: What Allah wills and Muhammad wills.\" The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, heard him and he said, \u201cDo not say: What Allah wills\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/02\/28\/make-me-partner-with-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":111,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: You make me a partner with Allah?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cWhat Allah wills and what you will.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHave you made me a partner with Allah? Rather, what Allah wills alone.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 783 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37278,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/31\/safeguarding-oaths-phrases\/","url_meta":{"origin":111,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Safeguarding words from lesser idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Qutaylah reported: A Jewish man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, you are setting up rivals with Allah and associating partners with Him when you say, \u2018What Allah wills and you will,\u2019 and when you swear by the Ka\u2019bah!\u201d Then the Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15329,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/allah-displeased-if-no-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":111,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Allah displeased with unmindful gatherings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people sit in a gathering without remembering Allah, or sending blessings upon their Prophet, but that they will earn the displeasure of Allah. If Allah wills, He will punish them. If He wills, He will forgive them.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24963,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/dua-affirm-hearts-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":111,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Guidance: O Allah, affirm our hearts upon Your religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: \u00a0I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how often you supplicate saying: O Turner of the hearts, keep my heart firm upon Your religion.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Umm Salamah, there is no human but that his heart is between\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11203,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/07\/sickness-tahur-in-sha-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":111,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sickness: Your illness is purification, if Allah wills","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: If the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the home of sick person to visit him, he would say, \"It will not harm you. It is purification, if Allah wills.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5332 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/111","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dail